{"id":151416,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/中南大学割喉案，这世界会好么？/","date":"2011-05-10T17:00:51Z","modified":"2011-05-10T17:00:51Z","title":"中南大学割喉案，这世界会好么？","content":"<p><p>@我是黄聪：中南大学升华公寓15栋附近，一个小时前一女生被男友砍死。<br />\n警察正在勘察现场。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img181.poco.cn/mypoco/myphoto/20110509/15/55946934201105091542073067854184519_029.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>该女生是中南大学外国语学院大二女生，凶手疑为该女生前男友，<br />\n出事前曾多次电话短信和死者联系，初步估计杀人动机为感情纠葛。（via:@郑无邪）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img181.poco.cn/mypoco/myphoto/20110509/15/55946934201105091542073067854184519_028.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>他没有机会再来到这里，也不会再见到他心爱的女友</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img181.poco.cn/mypoco/myphoto/20110509/15/55946934201105091542073067854184519_033.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>@三湘虢小灿：今天（8日）下午三点半左右，长沙中南大学升华学生公寓15.16栋之间，<br />\n一男子持刀杀害该校外国语学院大二女生后自杀。<br />\n女生被割~喉当场死亡，男子送医院抢救，肚子、脖子上多处伤口，目前有民警守在病房。</p>\n<p>图：男子从抢救室被往送病房</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img181.poco.cn/mypoco/myphoto/20110509/15/55946934201105091542073067854184519_025.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>如果您的阅读器看不到图片或视频，请移步原文链接：<a href=\"http://letaoba.info/archives/2099.html\">中南大学割喉案，这世界会好么？</a><br />\n<br />本文发表于 <a href=\"http://letaoba.info\">乐淘吧</a><br />\n<br /><a href=\"http://letaoba.info/subscribe\">欢迎订阅关注乐淘吧</a></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://www.taobao.com/go/chn/tbk_channel/huangguan.php?pid=mm_14340546_0_0&#038;eventid=101858\"><br />\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://letaoba.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/1.png\" /><br />\n</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://store.taobao.com/shop/view_shop.htm?user_number_id=188124207&#038;ref=&#038;ali_trackid=2:mm_14340546_0_0:136425500_41_1626768716\"><br />\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://letaoba.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/tangshi.png\" /><br />\n</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"http://store.taobao.com/shop/view_shop.htm?user_number_id=94246074&#038;ref=&#038;ali_trackid=2:mm_14340546_0_0:136426091_44_1626776486\"><br />\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://letaoba.info/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/fangcao.png\" /